  "Klingon Disruptor Rifle
   The Klingon disruptor rifle is a standard hand held disruptor, attached to an extended power supply stock. This serves to steady the aim of a warrior and increase the effective range for distance targeting."[1]

This word is used when referring to torpedoes, and is distinct from {bach:v}.

The suffix {-Daq:n} marks the target.

